Build instructions:
- Install arm-none-eabi toolchain
- Download and build the flasher - https://github.com/utzig/lm4tools
- Download StellarisWare library from Texas Instruments - link http://www.ti.com/tool/sw-ek-lm4f120xl
- Edit FLASHER directory on Makefile
- Edit STELLARISWARE_PATH directory on Makefile

To enabling GDB debug
- Follow the instructions to build OpenOCD from here http://processors.wiki.ti.com/index.php/Stellaris_Launchpad_with_OpenOCD_and_Linux
then update the ek-lm4f120xl.cfg directoy on gdb_load file.
